[[Fiend|fiend]]s and [[undead]] suffer additional [[radiant damage|damage type]] when struck by this weapon. These creatures may also become frightened of you when you strike them.

While you hold this weapon, it sheds bright light in a 20-foot radius and dim light for an additional 20 feet.